OL,3,CThousands of children wait years for
OL,4,Cautism support
OL,6,FThousands of autistic children and
OL,7,Fyoung people are waiting months - or
OL,8,Feven years - for health and eduction
OL,9,Fsupport, a new report has revealed.
OL,11,FParents are instead being left to
OL,12,Fnavigate a complex support system
OL,13,Fwhich is made worse by processing
OL,14,Fdelays and waiting as the number of
OL,15,Fchildren accessing autism services
OL,16,Fhits at a record high.
