OL,3,CThousands of children wait years for
OL,4,Cautism support
OL,6,FThe report by the initiative led by
OL,7,Fthe N8 research partnership and the
OL,8,Fthink tank has now called for a 'needs-
OL,9,Fled' approach instead of relying on a
OL,10,F'diagnosis-led' system.
OL,12,FThis, it says, will lead to early
OL,13,Fidentification becoming the norm, and
OL,14,Ffaster effective support offered
OL,15,Fwithout relying on a diagnosis.
