OL,3,CThousands of children wait years for
OL,4,Cautism support
OL,6,FEarly identification and support can
OL,7,Falso mitigate the negative and costly
OL,8,Feffects on autistic children's
OL,9,Fphysical health.JThe report highlights
OL,10,Fhow since Covid-19 there has been a
OL,11,F306% increase in the number of
OL,12,Fchildren waiting for an autism
OL,13,Fassessment.
OL,15,FJust one in 10 children are receiving
OL,16,Fan appointment within 13 weeks of
OL,17,Fbeing referred, while more than one in
OL,18,Ffour parents have waited more than
OL,19,Fthree years to receive support for
OL,20,Ftheir child.
