OL,3,CThousands of children wait years for
OL,4,Cautism support
OL,6,FThe report's analysis reveals a system
OL,7,Funder unsustainable pressure.
OL,9,FThe report warns that the failure to
OL,10,Fprovide the right autism support can
OL,11,Flead to poor long-term outcomes for
OL,12,Fautistic children, including an
OL,13,Fincreased prevalence of connected
OL,14,Fconditions such as mental ill health
OL,15,Fand a greater risk of school exclusion
OL,16,For not attending school.
