OL,3,CThousands of children wait years for
OL,4,Cautism support
OL,6,FData from the Connected Bradford
OL,7,Fdatabase included in the report
OL,8,Freveals that children who had been
OL,9,Freferred but were still waiting for an
OL,10,Fassessment were at greatest risk of
OL,11,Fbeing excluded from secondary school.
OL,13,FAutistic children who had a diagnosis
OL,14,Fwere less likely to be excluded from
OL,15,Fschool, compared to those awaiting an
OL,16,Fassessment, suggesting a diagnosis and
OL,17,Fsubsequent support has a protective
OL,18,Feffect.
