OL,3,CThousands of children wait years for
OL,4,Cautism support
OL,6,FGiven the long waiting lists, many
OL,7,Fautistic children are not receiving
OL,8,Fthe support they need because they do
OL,9,Fnot have a formal diagnosis.
OL,11,F"The number of autistic children
OL,12,Fseeking support is at a record high
OL,13,Fand the number waiting for an
OL,14,Fassessment has rocketed since Covid,"
OL,15,Fsaid Anne Longfield, Executive Chair
OL,16,Fof the Centre for Young Lives.
