OL,3,CThousands of children wait years for
OL,4,Cautism support
OL,6,F"The autism assessment crisis is
OL,7,Fleaving thousands of children without
OL,8,Fthe support they need and parents
OL,9,Fhaving to battle their way through a
OL,10,Fnightmare process that can take years
OL,11,Fto resolve.
OL,13,F"The pressure and stress this is
OL,14,Fputting on families and children can
OL,15,Fhave terrible and damaging
OL,16,Fconsequences for mental health and for
OL,17,Fchildren's education chances.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
